{"tid":1802992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角男墮樓倒臥後巷 昏迷送院不治","createTime":"2019-12-30T01:10:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T01:50:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec1a909ca71de7074427ac2e4da9b2bda25411c","tid":1802992,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:10:00.000Z","msg":"一名38歲男子昨晚在旺角墮樓，倒臥山東街一後巷，昏迷送院不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方昨晚7時53分接獲途人報案，指聽到一聲巨響，之後發現事主倒臥山東街18號一後巷，懷疑從高處墮下。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，事主昏迷被送往廣華醫院治理，之後被證實死亡。警方於其身上沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信事主從甘霖街37號一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1669536/即時-港聞-旺角38歲男墮樓倒臥後巷-昏迷送院不治</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bc59f1c084692313eb03a02056c7ee0d2614d0b8","tid":1802992,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205f7e443a7d325bc8cae1173edbfc5c493d0541","tid":1802992,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:27:04.000Z","msg":"屌你又冇可疑"},{"pid":"0362863385512330d6f0bfe81ceb03bb229c57f0","tid":1802992,"uid":196964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"屌 成日話無可疑"},{"pid":"b082c5720bbf869ad8b19dfc95d4fdaa59aca404","tid":1802992,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T01:50:36.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}